default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultthe JCHR consider the proposals to restrict legal aid in the wider cont
defaultext of legal aid, including any measure to restrict representative 
defaultgroups from bringing applications for judicial review;
default&#xa0;
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultthe JC
defaultHR seeks evidence from the Minis
defaulttry of Justice as to how the proposed scheme will work and the impact that the proposed require
defaultments are like
defaultly to have on access to justice;
default&#xa0;
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe JCHR concludes that the residence test must not be brought into force.
